WEBVTT

00:04:59.528 --> 00:05:01.149
They could trust their colleagues.

00:05:01.173 --> 00:05:03.313
They didn't need to look
behind their backs.

00:05:04.293 --> 00:05:06.627
And they were basically having fun.

00:05:06.651 --> 00:05:08.452
They were having so much fun,

00:05:08.476 --> 00:05:10.660
one guy even confessed

00:05:10.684 --> 00:05:14.034
that he was having more fun
at the company Christmas dinner

00:05:14.058 --> 00:05:15.866
than at his own Christmas dinner.

00:05:15.890 --> 00:05:18.111
(Laughter)

00:05:18.135 --> 00:05:23.216
But these guys, essentially,
were working in a fair system

00:05:23.240 --> 00:05:25.802
where they could do
what they felt was right

00:05:25.826 --> 00:05:28.636
instead of what's selfish,
what's quick, what's convenient,

00:05:28.660 --> 00:05:31.537
and to be able to do what we feel is right